title: A Slovak town Gulf tourists fell in love with
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary: Piešťany, one of several spa towns in Slovakia, is unique in several aspects. Mike Valek from Cardiff has lived there for four years. He joins Peter Dlhopolec to disclose what life in Piešťany is all about.
